@captainboggles: Agreed! I saw the original after the one, and while good, this is better (also being in color is a bonus.) I liked how the characters are developed before they get to the locale, explaining why they are in such a place (also their previous occupations become essential to completing their mission.)

I only uploaded this just over a month ago... I was amazed that it wasn't here already given how recent/good it was, but when released it suffered from bad timing and was unexpectedly eclipsed by Star Wars so mostly forgotten.

If you liked it, I'm always happy to get a "+". ;^)
